  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to BattleTanks!</strong></h2>Defend the animal world against nefarious moles in a dynamic co-op action game teeming with tanks and animals!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/71c810392c1067be1b4d34a4087deb52.poster.avif?t=1736517628\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/71c810392c1067be1b4d34a4087deb52.webm?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/71c810392c1067be1b4d34a4087deb52.mp4?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Two unique perspectives!</strong></h2>Seamlessly switch between twin-stick shooter and first-person shooter perspectives!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/eb42ef920d5e042275ca8a2eef4c2f12.poster.avif?t=1736517628\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/eb42ef920d5e042275ca8a2eef4c2f12.webm?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/eb42ef920d5e042275ca8a2eef4c2f12.mp4?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Campain Mode!</strong></h2>Explore 5 Vibrant Worlds with over 80 Missions, featuring Arena battles, Defense missions, Side-Scroller challenges, and Puzzles!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/ea426311c9a6b66c0f58e9227ab3fcd2.poster.avif?t=1736517628\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/ea426311c9a6b66c0f58e9227ab3fcd2.webm?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/ea426311c9a6b66c0f58e9227ab3fcd2.mp4?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenging Bosses!</strong></h2>Overcome the challenge of five Great Mecha Beasts in your path.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/3dadac28ee9bf77ecc1e8043293fcc61.poster.avif?t=1736517628\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/3dadac28ee9bf77ecc1e8043293fcc61.webm?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/3dadac28ee9bf77ecc1e8043293fcc61.mp4?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Co-op up to 4 players</strong></h2>Gather your pals and dive into some couch co-op or competitive gaming action!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/97da3edde71c64b169e9e3203bc88c72.poster.avif?t=1736517628\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/97da3edde71c64b169e9e3203bc88c72.webm?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/97da3edde71c64b169e9e3203bc88c72.mp4?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Arcade Modes!</strong></h2>Go head-to-head with your friends across 11 various arcade challenges such as  <br>Deathmatch, Capture the Flag, Destroy Base, Survival, Duel, Bombarding,  Crazy Tunnels, <br>Boss Rush, and more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/2485427597c1f792e8cc7a5ea9f851ee.poster.avif?t=1736517628\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/2485427597c1f792e8cc7a5ea9f851ee.webm?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/2485427597c1f792e8cc7a5ea9f851ee.mp4?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make your own Tank</strong></h2>Make your own unique Tank and use one of 13 deadly weapons!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/8a93be17f9fd45700c14b06539875bf5.poster.avif?t=1736517628\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/8a93be17f9fd45700c14b06539875bf5.webm?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881720/extras/8a93be17f9fd45700c14b06539875bf5.mp4?t=1736517628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiple game modes<br></li><li>Fun and extremely catchy graphics<br></li><li>Unique campaign mode<br></li><li>Arcade action modes<br></li><li>3D pixel perfect maps<br></li><li>80+ maps<br></li><li>Side scroller stages<br></li><li>BOSS fights!<br></li><li>Up to 4 players on your couch<br></li><li>Fully customizable tanks and weapons<br></li><li>Funny heroes and various enemies</li></ul>",
